<i>adjective</i>: 거슴츠레하다 [거슴츠레하다] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>adjective</i><br>
<dt>거슴츠레하다 [거슴츠레하다]</dt><br>
<dd>bleary-eyed</dd><br>
<dd>졸리거나 술에 취해 눈빛이 멍하고 눈이 거의 감길 듯하다.</dd><br>
<dd>A person's eyes being dull and half-closed as if he/she is sleepy or drunk.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>